%C A038608 a(n) is the determinant of the (n+1) X (n+1) matrix with 0's in the main diagonal and 1's elsewhere. - _Franz Vrabec_, Dec 01 2007
%C A038608 Sum_{n>0} 1/a(n) = -log(2). - _Jaume Oliver Lafont_, Feb 24 2009
